HEADWORD: magic trick
<hw>magic trick</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>An feat of illusion performed by
an illusionist, which appears magical to naive observers.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> conjuring trick, trick, magic, legerdemain,
illusion, deception.</syn>⟦br⟧
